headline.main: Liz Weston: 9 Bills Where You Can Cut a Better Deal
headline.print_headline: Liz Weston: 9 Bills Where You Can Cut a Better Deal

lead_paragraph: The word "bills" used to be synonymous with "fixed expenses." But there's nothing fixed about many of the bills a typical household pays today.
